Package: forkflow
Title: A Reproducible Workflow for Multiverse and Vibration-of-Effects Analyses
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alyssa", "Columbus", email = "alyssahcolumbus@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to build, run, summarise, and report multiverse and
    vibration-of-effects analyses in R. Enumerate a grid of defensible analytic
    specifications, fit a model across the whole grid (optionally in parallel),
    and summarise the resulting distribution of estimates with specification
    curves and vibration-of-effects volcano plots. Motivated by trustworthy
    data analysis in large observational epidemiological studies.
